Info.Title: The New Mutants
Info.Writer: Josh Boone, Knate Lee, Chris Claremont (based on the Marvel comics by), Bob McLeod (based on the Marvel comics by), Len Wein (character created by: Magik), Dave Cockrum (character created by: Magik)
Info.Actors: Anya Taylor-Joy, Maisie Williams, Antonio Banderas, Alice Braga
Info.Plot: Five young mutants, just discovering their abilities while held in a secret facility against their will, fight to escape their past sins and save themselves.
